Text:
@Pho_Q and anyone else getting this error message.

The error doesn't matter. It happened to me too, but that file isn't important because it's replaced by the crack file from the crack directory.

Just tell it to keep going/ignore the error and when it's done, copy the crack into the folder you installed it to ("C:\Program Files\Rollercoaster Tycoon 2\" by default) and the game will work just fine.
